From c920b2d16d7c90f8d7a85d0dbb04adc8e2d68e48 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Work Leaf Bench <bench@example.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 21:25:39 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] ADD selected-agent slash commands for backend-only
 execution

Route selected-agent chat that begins with a slash command token through AgentBackend command execution so backend commands append command output in chat and do not reach the ordinary send/resume prompt path. Codex implements /status and /fork from known session state.
